                        <item xml:id="a22">
                           <locus target="#Loose bits of paper">-Loose bits of paper</locus>
                           <desc>Loose folio</desc>
                           <q>Fragments of a text</q>
                           <note>There are five bits of paper that have text on one side. The paper has blue vertical rulings. The text is written in the same hand and the bits probably belong together.  The text may be a letter.</note>
                        </item>
